description:
HMB TOKEN will build communication infrastructure and payment and payment platform to support the realization of SMART CITY PROJECT worldwide, and will be in charge of the core role in the city.
In addition, IOT will connect to urban infrastructure in the ENERGY and WELFARE areas based on IOT, solve many urban problems and raise the quality of life.
HMB will generate financial returns, and it will be a good token in anticipation of its own rising value. In addition, it is expected to be applied to actual life as a cryptocurrency linked to the wallet with MOBIDOLLAR.
